" Increment/decrement
nnoremap + <C-a>
nnoremap - <C-x>

" Save with root permission
command! W w !sudo tee > /dev/null %

" deactivate highlight
nmap <silent><Esc><Esc> :nohl<Return>

"-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
" Tabs
"-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
" タブ移動は <C-PageDown> / <C-PageUp> で出来る
" タブ移動
nmap <C-PageDown> :tabnext<Return>
nmap <C-PageUp> :tabprevious<Return>
" タブ並び替え (chromeライクなキーマップ)
nmap <C-S-PageDown> :+tabmove
nmap <C-S-PageUp> :-tabmove

"-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
" Windows
"-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
" Resize window
nmap <C-w><left> <C-w><
nmap <C-w><right> <C-w>>
nmap <C-w><up> <C-w>+
nmap <C-w><down> <C-w>-
